text: Jørund Henning Rytman (born 4 May 1977) is a Norwegian Progress Party politician representing Buskerud in the Storting. He was first elected in 2005. ==Storting committees== *2013–2017 member of the Business and Industry committee *2009–2013 member of the Finance and Economic Affairs committee *2005–2009 member of the Finance and Economic Affairs committee ==External links== * *Fremskrittspartiet - Biography *Rytman.no - Official Homepage Category:Progress Party (Norway) politicians Category:Members of the Storting Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian Christians Category:21st-century Norwegian politicians
